# flask-s3-uploader-288950

AWS configuration utilities for Python applications.

## Installation

```bash
pip install flask-s3-uploader-288950
```

## Usage

```python
from flask_s3_uploader_288950 import get_config, get_client

# Get AWS configuration
config = get_config()

# Get S3 client
s3 = get_client('s3')
```
